'''Grindelwald''' is a [[Wikipedia:Municipalities of Switzerland|municipality]] in the district of [[Wikipedia:Interlaken (district)|Interlaken]] in the [[Wikipedia:Cantons of Switzerland|canton]] of [[Wikipedia:Bern (canton)|Bern]] in [[Wikipedia:Switzerland|Switzerland]]. Although no actual filming took place there, its [[mountain]]s were scouted for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']] to capture plate photography for backdrops on the [[planet]] [[Alderaan]].

